Driver Class Name: oracle.jdbc.driver.OracleDriver --> in older Version
                            or
                    oracle.jdbc.OracleDriver   --> for newer version
                    
URL: jdbc.oracle.oci8:@xe  --> older Version
      jdbc.oracle.oci:@xe  --> for newer Version
                        |
                        |
                    System ID --> Every Database has Unique id as SID
                    
to identify SID:

1. select * from global_name;
2. tnsnames.ora